// Regression: heap-mode INVOKESTATIC must pop arguments from the
// caller's operand stack before saving the frame. Without the fix,
// each call leaks num_args slots on the caller's stack. This test
// exercises multiple sequential INVOKESTATIC calls from the main body
// to verify values aren't corrupted. Stack overflow from the leak
// would require 500+ calls and is not tested here.
: dup 1 pick ;
: noop ;
: dec 1 - ;
: fact dup 1 swap < if go else base ;
: go dup dec fact * ;
: base drop 1 ;
5 fact print
6 fact print
